    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クロエ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chloe</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>オイ、コラ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おまえが寝坊して船出さなかったせいで
１００年に一度のチャンスを
逃がしちまったじゃねぇかよ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We missed the boat 'cause you overslept,
and now we've lost out on a once every
hundred years chance!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>今日は１００年に一度の
女の子大集合水着祭りだったんだぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Today was a huge once in a century
gathering for a ladies' swimsuit festival!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>せっかく絶好の
見物ポイントを設置したってのに！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And we had even figured out
the perfect sightseeing point!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>こいつら……馬鹿だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These guys... are idiots.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、馬鹿だ。
騎士として女性として
こんな奴らを野放しには出来ない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Idiots, indeed. As a knight and a woman,
I will not let them do as they please!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なら決まりだな。
いくぞ、クロエ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then we've got ourselves a course of action.
Let's go, Chloe!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ！
今回は心置きなく戦える！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right!
I can fight with no reservations this time!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
